                    {
                      "id": "87ebb3f",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At the forefront of this regenerative movement stood Joshua Hughes, a visionary entrepreneur dedicated to redefining ethical modern businesses. </span><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshua-hughes-68a338169/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://www.linkedin.com/in/joshua-hughes-68a338169/</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /></span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IG: </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Joshuahughes_rewild</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2006, Joshua initiated the creation of Verdenergia, a permaculture farm in Costa Rica with regenerative pratices. Little did he know that this would be the beginning of a transformative journey filled with valuable lessons and profound impact.</span></p>",
                        "align": "justify",
                        "_margin": {
                          "unit": "px",
