                    },
                    {
                      "id": "f3292a5",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Verdenergia quickly gained momentum, rallying over 4000 people to join their cause of reforesting a patch of land in Costa Rica. This collective effort not only regenerated the landscape but also improved the local community and inspired others to embark on similar journeys in their own regions.</span></p>",
