                    }
                  ],
                  "isInner": true
                },
                {
                  "id": "04b8725",
                  "elType": "column",
                  "settings": {
                    "_column_size": 50,
                    "_inline_size": null
                  },
                  "elements": [
                    {
                      "id": "d9e2cd8",
                      "elType": "widget",
                      "settings": {
                        "editor": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Everywhere you dig, you can see a deep dark, earthy smelling soil hosting a myriad of different trees and spieces. Walkin with Steven, Permaculture designer, he explains how he sees Vetiver as a tremendous pionneer spieces for soil regeneration. The Vetiver System, with its deep-rooted and resilient Vetiver grass, not only prevented soil erosion but also acted as a natural barrier against runoff, allowing the land to heal and flourish. Through the strategic use of Vetiver, Verdenergia showcased a harmonious blend of regenerative agriculture and eco-friendly practices, setting a precedent for sustainable land management.</span></p>"
                      },
                      "elements": [],
                      "widgetType": "text-editor"
                    }
                  ],
                  "isInner": true
                }
              ],
              "isInner": true
            },
            {
              "id": "c6c01bc",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Impact on the Community",
                "align": "center",
                "_margin": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "top": "10",
                  "right": "10",
                  "bottom": "10",
                  "left": "10",
                  "isLinked": true
                }
              },
              "elements": [],
              "widgetType": "heading"
            },
            {
              "id": "16ea900",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The transition from barren pastures to flourishing food jungle gardens stands as a testament to the success of Verdenergia's regenerative projects. By engaging local farmers and the community of Lana, Verdenergia not only reclaimed natural landscapes but also became a beacon of inspiration for sustainable and ethical agricultural practices in the region.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sixteen years later, Verdenergia stands strong as a top permaculture and agroforestry education centers. Through its initiatives like Rewild Organic, it continues to shape a more harmonious coexistence with nature.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Don’t miss the opportunity to learn at one of their Permaculture Design Course. </span></p><p><a href=\"https://verdenergia.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https://verdenergia.org/</span></a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As the world grapples with the challenges of sustainability, Verdenergia stands as a shining example of what is possible when communities unite for a common goal – cultivating sustainable futures for generations to come.</span></p>"
              },
              "elements": [],
              "widgetType": "text-editor"
